  • Classes in com.tectonica.jonix.stream used by com.tectonica.jonix 
    Class and Description
    JonixExtractor
    An abstract base-class for an extractor - a listener for JonixStreamer processing the events it fires as it parses an ONIX source.
    JonixFilesExtractor
    Simple extension of JonixExtractor adding events related for file-processing, fired by a JonixFilesStreamer.
    JonixFilesStreamer
    Simple extension of JonixStreamer that adds some APIs for handling ONIX sources stored in files and directories (and not just InputStream as the parent).
    JonixStreamer
    This is a fundamental class in Jonix.
